，剩係係街見到同聽人講都知有咁多衰嘢，真實有幾咁閪真係難以想像"},{"pid":"99f17826e974e6c93349b70e2f439130286f82d6","tid":2186944,"uid":266467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:23:16.000Z","msg":"樓主啱啱被地盤佬兇完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cffaf5291c4d4b8344436ab5900d06ef7c117d8","tid":2186944,"uid":99973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:55:27.000Z","msg":"無錢就枱唔起頭<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">岸鳩仔</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"14000edfeea7ece59903341970bf3d340b53be29","tid":2186944,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2d2ea6db4c34c2a73d8d8f130eb0ab8d9def588","tid":2186944,"uid":53705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:39:39.000Z","msg":"我就係做左地盤十年<br />\n<br />\n老實講句,  根本多數都係讀唔成書, 先要做地盤 (包括我)<br />\n讀到書, 根本無人想做地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋我唔明白點解成日有人吹捧 地盤 呢一行<br />\n日日話咩職安真漢子, 真係笑死人<br />\n<br />\n事實上地盤佬好多都心胸狹窄<br />\n成日係到講事講非, 單單打打<br />\n日日聽到討厭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579eded38e0041e49b4b9962ab2bf5b178b37e52","tid":2186944,"uid":181502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a264052019ba280bc7455281b7726ae25b3895d","tid":2186944,"uid":122134,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:09:12.000Z","msg":"如果做到頂層就係既<br />\n但如果岩岩由地下開始起<br />\n要係咁向上望<br />\n抬到頸都累"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:18:44.000Z","msg":"樓主hang能咗機😂"}]}